      • addInstanceListener

        <KeyClass,InstanceType extends KeyClass> void addInstanceListener(java.lang.Class<KeyClass> key,
                                                                InstanceListener<KeyClass> listener)
        Add a listener that will be triggered when a specific class is added to the handler. If the specific class is already present in the handler, then the listener will be triggered immediately.
        Parameters:
        key - the class to listen for
        listener - the listener to be triggered
